! Aperture-stop sizing: a flat air-air "dummy" surface marked STO must report
! its real clear aperture (the beam footprint), not 0.  Regression for the
! Bentley5p5 case (check_clear_apertures used to skip dummy surfaces).
LEN NEW
TIT 'StopApertureTest'
EPD 10.0
INS S2..5
RDY S1         60
THI S1         6
GLA S1         NSK16_SCHOTT
RDY S2         -150
THI S2         18
THI S3         18
STO S3
RDY S4         150
THI S4         6
GLA S4         NSK16_SCHOTT
RDY S5         -60
PIM
CLI
